{"tid":2351931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當局巡查外傭聚集地點，共發出51張告票","createTime":"2021-01-03T15:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T16:25:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0708817966d9624b944ca3bd3e72512e2150ac","tid":2351931,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568418-20210103.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568418-20210103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0JnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=d116798f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568418-20210103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0cad1751\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568418-20210103.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n勞工處聯同警方及食環署等多個部門，新年假期期間在外傭經常聚集的地方採取聯合行動，呼籲他們遵守限聚令及口罩令。截至今日第一階段截算時間為止的4天期間，聯合行動共發出51張5千元定額罰款通知書。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人說，按現場觀察，絕大部分外傭及市民經勸喻後均遵守有關規定，例如在今日的聯合行動中，旺角花園街附近行人天橋上的外傭經勸喻後自行離去；至於有些屢經勸喻仍不遵守規定的人士，相關部門已採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n政府未來仍會繼續加強宣傳和執法，並會按需要採取聯合行動，以確保有關規定得以遵從。"},{"pid":"726d01ea8765c50a7148fb0340640acbf6f1a17b","tid":2351931,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"正乞衣"},{"pid":"7624ae5f575bc8840d4ff576bebed455b7e033f3","tid":2351931,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"白做幾個月"},{"pid":"be13922782e6a8758da677492ecdee70fb62b758","tid":2351931,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"一早要啦"},{"pid":"e609e65f30eba0390bd6ca0cc0bbccd7a7a1e0f9","tid":2351931,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"得51張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全港肯定有超過51個地方俾d賓賓佔領左"}